{"tid":2343163,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Asrock x570m pro4網絡問題","createTime":"2020-12-27T17:17:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T00:38:02.000Z","uid":133379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c9c3171915662fc049f61599226e1e7b338d0f69","tid":2343163,"uid":133379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T17:17:44.000Z","msg":"第一次開post <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n說話小弟今年五月個陣upgrade pc<br />\n買咗x570m pro4 ，3700x  同adata 3200mhz<br />\n之後就一陣都出事 有時開機入到windows話冇咗network adapter 出事嘅時候重裝唔到network driver 重新開機都冇用 update哂啲bios driver 都冇用<br />\n試過重裝windows都照出事 但奇怪在 唔係次次開機都有問題  睇過外國網友都有呢個問題 所以想睇連登大大們有冇解決方法<br />\n<br />\n個問題解決方法有兩個<br />\n1.拔底板電<br />\n<br />\n2. Reset bios 後關機拔火牛線<br />\n<br />\n困擾咗好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />感謝連登大大們"},{"pid":"58d537c238e8a06e78d4b57643b45851002bd9ef","tid":2343163,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T17:33:42.000Z","msg":"深夜召喚硬件傳心師，Gd luck<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比個提示你：自行google"},{"pid":"e95eb5756860315a88d6045b7959e2b5f72f44c1","tid":2343163,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T00:38:02.000Z","msg":"network adapter = lan port driver <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}